snippet.title: Pocket Battles: NFT War Trailer (ENG)
snippet.description: "Pocket Battles: NFT War" is the World's Best Strategy Battle P2E game. The game is free-to-play where you can earn COINS everyday without buying NFT. NFT holders can compete in Pocket Championship to win $200,000 prize every quarter.
